UnlockDescription.LocalizedString: The new survivor is Mikaela Reid, a cheerful barista blessing coffee by day and telling fortunes by night. Her keen interest in witchcraft nourishes her creative soul and keeps her inspired. Every Friday night, she performs stories at the Moonstone, the independent coffee shop where she works. But when she steps on the stage at the Endless Halloween storytelling competition, her tale of horror takes an unexpected dark turn.
